    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/37b83ebc45d734c702760a9766839cff.avif?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/3a5a017407cca5683448469ad4f66336.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/eea7f57e8e11e497a107709f30edca77.avif?t=1761840248\" width=614 height=345 /></span><br><br>尼德霍格的追随者是生命的消耗者，他们利用奴隶来满足他们贪婪的经济需求，并通过人类献祭来生产邪恶的龙之精华。这种邪恶的力量最终会把他们变成可怕的龙族，暴露出他们的非人本性。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/320b5ed093d31497f453dc05937d813d.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/fb43053d421e87280908d791bc182cdc.avif?t=1761840248\" width=614 height=220 /></span><br><br>可怕而严酷的苏尔特尔使用暴力接管了龙族。他是独臂的末日使者，出现在穆斯佩尔的火焰之中，直到火焰覆盖了埃西尔的土地，才会停下来。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/23a1b4503bc67fe1446dfa2111735422.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/0aea3e3fd2e4bfb3988babd42028d37a.poster.avif?t=1761840248\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/0aea3e3fd2e4bfb3988babd42028d37a.webm?t=1761840248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/0aea3e3fd2e4bfb3988babd42028d37a.mp4?t=1761840248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>尼德霍格祭祀的柴堆是他们力量的象征。他们通过献出奴隶作为祭品，获得他们神明的祝福。只要献祭仍在继续，他们也愿意牺牲自己。如果不这样做，这种力量就可能会从他们手中溜走，并在不久后引发反抗。<br><br>通过在祭坛上举行古老仪式，将龙之精华注入普通村民身上使他们成为名为龙族的凶猛战士。谁知道那仪式会对他们的人性造成什么影响……又有哪些潜在的可能呢。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/ec21cd387d9376e65ff8db4a4534bec8.avif?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/633245896b5c13e9f70aa1d72db68e30.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你以祭祀的柴堆起家，它会为你提供暂时的奖励，但需要定期的祭祀。<br></li><li>你可以建造一个龙族祭坛而不是其他的军事营地。<br></li><li>你一开始便有奴隶，他们会收集食物，并可以被分配到建筑以增加工人产量。<br></li><li> 你的平民可以进入中立领土，并且不会因为受伤而受到幸福度或生产量惩罚。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/ea0d842fcb363f83d3facb9712388761.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><strong>声望200：不情愿的劳动力</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>获得新的奴隶。你的龙之精华槽会拓展，奖励会增加。</li></ul><br><strong>声望500：宿怨</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以通过第二次将龙族送到龙族祭坛，来训练龙之噩梦。<br></li><li>你的龙之精华槽将拓展至最大值，并增加奖励的价值。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/4018d3eae30139d235a3ca1ad8302cf7.webp?t=1761840248\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971630/extras/6846a4ef152ca888a9fcaefb24a8c7eb.avif?t=1761840248\" width=614 height=220 /></span><br><br>召唤一个狂暴霜巨人。",
